\subsection{Critic learning dynamics}
The most direct measure of the critic's learning process is its training loss: the mean squared error between its value predictions and the GAE-computed returns. The dynamics of this process are visualized in Figure~\ref{fig:critic_loss_plot}, and key statistics are summarized in Table~\ref{tab:critic_loss}.

\begin{figure}[h!]
